text: East Livermore is an unincorporated village in the town of Livermore Falls, Androscoggin County, Maine, United States. The community is located along Maine State Route 133 and the Androscoggin River north of Lewiston. East Livermore has a post office with ZIP code 04228. ==References== Category:Villages in Androscoggin County, Maine Category:Villages in Maine
title: East Livermore, Maine
